Mikeotizels HTTP Error Pages - ChangeLog
========================================

2.0.0 (2022-05-10)
------------------

- Added more error documents for other standard 4xx and 5xx response codes as 
  defined by RFC 9110: 402, 406, 407, 409, 416, 417, 422, 423, 424, 504, 505, 
  507, and 510.
- Modified some error description messages to make them more informative.
- Updated the HTML markup for the error documents from HTML 4 to HTML 5.
- Added custom inline CSS code and changed the overall error page layout.
- Added a footer section with author signature and mail link with the server 
  admin email address where the visitor may report the error encountered.

1.0.0 (2021-01-15)
------------------

- Initial release